Thank you for allowing Rollins Acceptance Company to service your purchase.
There is no penalty for paying your purchase off early. Interest is calculated only on the principle. You may obtain payoff information on the website or contact us at 1-800-437-5641.
Please allow eight (8) business days for mail-in payments along with processing time to ensure your payment is posted by your due date. Payments incurred after your due date will incur a late fee.

Thank you for allowing Rollins Acceptance Company (a division of Rollins, Inc) to manage your purchase.
You’re approved for 90 Days Same as Cash.
The total purchase amount must be received and posted to your account on or before your first due date listed below to avoid any accrued interest charges.
You may also choose to make payments. There is no penalty for paying your purchase off early. Interest is calculated only on the principle. You may obtain payoff information on the website or contact us at 1-800-437-5641.
Please allow eight (8) business days for mail-in payments along with processing time to ensure your payment is posted by your due date.
